// Lightbox content data
const lightboxSections = [
  {
    text: "These images were generated as I began development on a community platform, Starscape's Earth Villages. It was born from a desire to help conscious communities — like those forming around festivals and retreats, and local communities with friends — deepen their sense of connection, presence and life experience. Starscape aims to support these communities beyond the moments of magic by providing a lasting digital home that reflects and extends their real-world values and relationships.",
  },
  {
    text: "At its core, Starscape Earth Villages is a modular, customizable platform for collective well-being and collaboration. Each village—whether tied to a geographic region, a seasonal gathering, or a shared intention—gets its own uniquely themed digital space. These portals support meaningful group chats, events, announcements, VOIP rooms, educational courses, storytelling, evolving maps, and potentially 3D scenes to 'live' in a world together.",
  },
  {
    text: "The platform is built to grow with its communities. With a regenerative design ethos and hired help, Starscape Earth Villages will enable affordable and private interconnection between local and global efforts without sacrificing uniqueness or sovereignty. Whether you're nurturing a village in the forest, a temple in the mountains, a scene in a city, or a crew of co-creators spread across the globe, Starscape helps anchor the shared spirit in a way that is beautiful, functional, and enduring.",
